{"meta":{"domain":"subjects","kid":"5292","authors":[{"fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre","id":"6"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:49 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:49 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">The marker <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span> (and its variants <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f66\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f4f\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span>) has locative (with or without movement) case functions. It also functions as adverbial suffix and marker of object incorporation.<\/p><p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Examples in the locative<\/em>:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f42\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cOn \/ to the left\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f42\u0f61\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cOn \/ to the right\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f62\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f42\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo go to India\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0fa1\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f97\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f42\u0fb3\u0f72\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f66\u0fa1\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo live in Darjeeling\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f51\u0f74\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cAt the time\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f4f\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f55\u0fb2\u0f7a\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cA rosary in the hand\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f55\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f74\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f56\u0f0b\u0f4f\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f66\u0f90\u0fb1\u0f74\u0f62\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo leave one\u2019s native land behind\u201d<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Examples of object incorporation<\/em>:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f51\u0f54\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f56\u0f62\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo be resplendent\u201d (Literally: \u201cTo blaze in glory\u201d) <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f50\u0f74\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f4f\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo shorten\u201d (Literally: \u201cTo send to small\u201d)<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Examples of adverbial use<\/em>:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0fb7\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f62\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cParticularly\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f44\u0f7a\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f62\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cAbsolutely\u201d<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">Note that the marker <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span> (and its variants), as well as the marker <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f0b<\/span> are associated with the adverb <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f47\u0f7a\u0f0b<\/span> \u201ceven more\u201d which is used only in the literary language. In the spoken language, the oblique case <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span> (or rather its variant <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span>) alone conveys this meaning.<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f47\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f55\u0f7a\u0f63\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo increase even more\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f51\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f5b\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f49\u0f7c\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f62\u0fa3\u0f58\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f9f\u0f7c\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f7c\u0f42\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f47\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f46\u0f74\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f47\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f46\u0f74\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f0d<\/span> \u201cSelfishness, negative emotions, discursive thought, and so on decrease even further.\u201d<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">The marker <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f51\u0f74\u0f0b<\/span> has connective functions when it is followed by a verb. It is also used to form purpose clauses.<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f66\u0fa8\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f66\u0fb3\u0f7c\u0f56\u0f0b\u0f4f\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f4f\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cTo send (someone) <strong>to <\/strong>learn Tibetan medicine\u201d<\/li> <\/ul>","title":""}]}